description:

name: Please Be Brave Zine
description: "Please Be Brave" Zine. I spent June drawing out this zine. It's 20 60 lb 6.5"x 8.5" Black & White Xeroxed Pages with a 80 lb Card Stock Cover Sheet. I just tried jamming as many things as I possibly could onto each page. I added two poems I like, but pretty much there's no words, just drawings of the things I like to draw. The first page is Dracula themed.

name: Zine Bundle Deal
description:
You can save on buying my 3 latest zines by buying them all at once.

You'll get these zines:
"I See All", A 8.5"x11" 32 page Alphabet Zine that took forever to make.
"They Come At Night" a 5.5"x7.5" a 20 page wordless narrative.
"Various Drawings 2012" 4.25 x 5.5" 40 page zine of favorites images of my work from 2012.

For $18 (Which is a savings of $5. or a little over 20% OFF) 

Sold Out of "They Come At Night". Will print more soon.

name: Lovin' You Drawing
description:
8.5" x11" Drawing in 9"x12" Frame. 
Drawing on Bristol, Signed in Back. Image from 2011. Drawing used for sticker image. 

Drawing is framed with archival backing and foam core in a 9"x12" Ikea frame.  

Ships Priority Mail (3-5 days US, 6-10 Internationally) in a box with extra padding. 
 
Shipping is a lot for international buyers. If you're an international buyer and would like this unframed, i can ship it in a stay-flat envelope for $10. You can message me if that interests you.
